<h5>Utilites <a href="#utilities">#</a></h5>
<p>DezUI provides some basic utility classes to speed up development</p>
<ul>
	<li><code>dm-serif</code> - <span class="dm-serif">DM Serif Display</span> font family.</li>
	<li><code>raleway</code> - Raleway font family.</li>
	<li><code>source-code-pro</code> - <span class="source-code-pro">Source Code Pro</span> font family.</li>
	<li><code>text-[Color Themes]</code> - Color of text</li>
	<li><code>bg-[Color Themes]</code> - Background color</li>
	<li><code>align-items-[All properties]</code></li>
	<li><code>text-align-[All properties]</code></li>
	<li><code>justify-content-[All properties]</code></li>
	<li><code>dotted</code> - for dotted style &lt;hr&gt;</li>
	<li><code>hero</code> - Give padding: 50px 0;</li>
	<li><code>hero hero-full</code> - Give padding: 50px 0px; and height: 100vh;</li>
	<li><code>width-[breakpoint properties]</code></li>
	<li><code>width-full</code></li>
	<li><code>col-margin-row | col</code> - Give margin 1rem top & bottom (col) or left & right (row).</li>
	<li><code>br-curve | round</code> - Give border-radius: 10px | 20px;</li>
	<li><code>m-0 | t | r | b | l | tb | lr | tb-0 | lr-0</code> - Margin 1rem</li>
	<li><code>p-0 | t | r | b | l | tb | lr | tb-0 | lr-0</code> - Pading 1rem</li>
	<li><code>position-[All properties]</code> - eg. static, fixed etc.</li>
</ul>
